1
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,960
I want Rin to work with me.

2
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:42,680
Holding people captive like that,

3
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:44,960
you could go to jail, Mr. Taiga.

4
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:46,800
Why are you stopping, Sun?

5
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:53,080
Anyone who betrays me
must die a painful death.

6
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:55,400
What are you doing here?

7
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:56,480
Just didn't want to say.

8
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,840
I asked, what are you doing here?

9
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,320
Take out the whole family.

10
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:37,960
Grab them, both mother and child.

11
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:47,480
People who enter someone's house
without permission,

12
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:50,080
that's called being rude.

13
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:54,120
What should happen to rude people?

14
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:31,560
Thank you so much.

15
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:35,720
Don't worry. Anything urgent,
just take care of it.

16
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,880
I'm sorry, Aru.

17
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:30,360
I'm sorry for what I did to you.

18
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,360
I never meant to do that to you.

19
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:37,000
Please forgive me, Aru.

20
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,520
I'm sorry.

21
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,920
Sun, what are you doing?

22
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:23,040
Techut ordered me to kill you.

23
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,880
But I didn't want to.

24
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:26,560
Does he know

25
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:28,840
we stole the medicine?

26
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,600
He suspects it.

27
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:33,160
The chemist said the vial is missing.

28
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,920
Does he know where Rin is?

29
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:38,160
I didn't tell him.

30
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,680
Thanks.

31
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:46,600
Aru.

32
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,600
I really didn't mean it.

33
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,280
In my life,

34
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,840
I only ever wanted to wrong you once.

35
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:56,280
You had to go to jail for me,

36
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:58,520
and now he wants me to kill you too.

37
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:00,680
I don't want to.

38
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:02,080
Tell me, Sun.

39
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:06,120
What has Techut forced you to do?

40
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:38,799
Attack 3C-Coin from every angle,

41
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:41,320
rumors, price manipulation, everything.

42
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:46,120
We'll mine it down
until it's worth nothing

43
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,360
but a single stone.

44
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,640
Start now.

45
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:08,840
Te.

46
00:09:08,920 --> 00:09:10,760
Don't ask. Just don't ask.

47
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:15,320
What, dear? Did the coin drop in price?

48
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:18,360
Hey! I said, don't ask!

49
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:22,000
Make yourself useful for once, Mom.

50
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:25,360
What do you want me to do, then?

51
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:27,880
Even for this, you can't figure it out.

52
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:30,240
Go wherever you want, sleep if you want.

53
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:32,400
I'm worried about you.

54
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,720
Don't worry.

55
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:36,440
I'm grown. I can take care of myself.

56
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:37,720
Te.

57
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:40,560
Were you too harsh just now?

58
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:43,440
I'll say it anyway. So what?

59
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:48,560
You want to remind me you're my mother,
carried me, gave birth, raised me?

60
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:50,560
That's your duty, isn't it?

61
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:52,400
The duty of a wife,

62
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:54,240
a wife my father never loved,

63
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:56,160
a wife he didn't want,

64
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:59,360
a wife he got by accident.

65
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:10,720
Drink this first. It'll calm you down.

66
00:10:17,640 --> 00:10:18,800
Done. Satisfied now?

67
00:10:21,400 --> 00:10:22,840
No matter how much you hate me,

68
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:25,080
or curse me,

69
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:28,000
I still love you.

70
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:31,240
My love

71
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:33,760
is like this cup of tea.

72
00:11:09,520 --> 00:11:11,120
Did Khanin take good care of you?

73
00:11:12,920 --> 00:11:13,920
Very good.

74
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:20,600
Well…

75
00:11:21,560 --> 00:11:23,480
Are you having any unusual symptoms?

76
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:33,080
No, I'm fine.

77
00:11:40,760 --> 00:11:42,520
INCOMING CALL

78
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:44,280
Answer it.

79
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:48,880
Whose number is this?

80
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:55,840
Uncle Punlop.

81
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:07,280
<i>Good to talk to you, Taiga.</i>

82
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:10,600
<i>How's my niece doing?</i>

83
00:12:11,280 --> 00:12:12,480
Rin.

84
00:12:13,760 --> 00:12:15,360
Aren't you going to greet your uncle?

85
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:20,600
Have you forgotten

86
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:22,480
who you are, Rin?

87
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:28,160
The one with you,

88
00:12:28,800 --> 00:12:30,240
the one who makes you hate me,

89
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:34,360
that's really someone you can love, right?

90
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:42,160
What do you want?

91
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:44,160
Do you want to know
who killed your father?

92
00:12:45,920 --> 00:12:46,920
<i>Don't you want to know</i>

93
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:49,720
why Khanin keeps following
and helping you?

94
00:12:51,160 --> 00:12:52,880
<i>People just keep moving forward.</i>

95
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:55,480
They can't leave
the past behind, can they?

96
00:12:58,200 --> 00:13:00,280
<i>Are you going to let Rin stay sick</i>

97
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:03,240
without proper medicine to fully heal

98
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:05,080
and get her body back to normal?

99
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:28,960
Don't go!

100
00:13:29,680 --> 00:13:30,960
Uncle Punlop will kill you.

101
00:13:42,920 --> 00:13:44,520
What excuse will you give now?

102
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:48,120
Mr. Taiga said

103
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:50,320
he was going to see Thai fabrics
at the weaving sites.

104
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:53,200
Where?

105
00:13:58,600 --> 00:14:01,720
If you're thinking about lying to me,
better start preparing yourself.

106
00:14:02,280 --> 00:14:04,320
Mom, that hurts!

107
00:14:04,400 --> 00:14:05,760
If it hurts, you bear it.

108
00:14:06,880 --> 00:14:09,320
The one who can bear more wins.

109
00:14:10,040 --> 00:14:11,160
Remember that.

110
00:14:20,680 --> 00:14:22,240
I'll call Mr. Taiga to come back.

111
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:23,320
No need.

112
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:26,960
I have better ways
to call our people back.

113
00:14:55,560 --> 00:14:57,520
How well do you know Uncle Punlop?

114
00:15:01,920 --> 00:15:03,120
Why do you ask?

115
00:15:16,800 --> 00:15:17,960
Choose, Taiga.

116
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:20,000
Choose for Rin.

117
00:15:21,400 --> 00:15:22,640
Cure her…

118
00:15:23,640 --> 00:15:24,680
or let her die.

119
00:16:26,480 --> 00:16:27,560
Thank you, my son,

120
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:30,280
for all your hard work for 3C Corp.

121
00:16:33,360 --> 00:16:35,000
Rest well.

122
00:16:36,240 --> 00:16:39,320
Your sister and I will handle the rest.

123
00:16:58,040 --> 00:16:59,960
I shouldn't have underestimated
the son of the Blazing Tiger.

124
00:17:01,040 --> 00:17:02,160
I thought you were skilled,

125
00:17:02,880 --> 00:17:06,240
but I didn't know you could forge
Rin's cold heart into daring betrayal.

126
00:17:10,200 --> 00:17:11,480
Rin isn't anyone's victim.

127
00:17:12,839 --> 00:17:14,119
Protecting,

128
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:15,440
taking the fall,

129
00:17:15,520 --> 00:17:17,400
even dying for one another now?

130
00:17:18,040 --> 00:17:19,480
Before, you nearly killed each other.

131
00:17:23,599 --> 00:17:24,680
You're ruthless.

132
00:17:24,760 --> 00:17:26,119
Can't help it.

133
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:29,200
A little bird struggles to escape.

134
00:17:33,800 --> 00:17:35,040
I must teach it a lesson.

135
00:17:42,480 --> 00:17:43,360
Come on, Taiga.

136
00:17:45,040 --> 00:17:46,560
Take the medicine and save Rin.

137
00:18:15,120 --> 00:18:17,960
3C's medicine is pricey.

138
00:18:19,320 --> 00:18:20,760
As pricey as your life.

139
00:18:33,720 --> 00:18:35,880
Just thinking about you, my dear niece.

140
00:18:35,960 --> 00:18:37,360
Punlop.

141
00:18:37,440 --> 00:18:38,840
Drop the gun.

142
00:18:40,440 --> 00:18:41,480
I said, drop it!

143
00:18:48,040 --> 00:18:50,240
Rin! Let go of her!

144
00:18:50,320 --> 00:18:51,440
- Go!
- Rin!

145
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:54,520
- You let her go, Punlop!
- He won't hurt Rin.

146
00:18:54,600 --> 00:18:56,120
- Go!
- Rin!

147
00:18:57,040 --> 00:18:58,600
- Punlop!
- Hey!

148
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:00,880
Go!

149
00:19:00,960 --> 00:19:02,000
Hey, the medicine!

150
00:19:03,280 --> 00:19:04,960
- Stay still.
- Let go!

151
00:19:12,320 --> 00:19:13,160
Khanin!

152
00:19:17,480 --> 00:19:19,000
Khanin, let go!

153
00:19:19,600 --> 00:19:21,440
- Follow them!
- Go!

154
00:19:21,520 --> 00:19:22,560
Follow them!

155
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:30,040
I told you before,

156
00:19:30,640 --> 00:19:31,960
the best chance…

157
00:19:33,320 --> 00:19:34,720
comes only once.

158
00:20:59,320 --> 00:21:00,280
Watch him carefully.

159
00:21:00,920 --> 00:21:03,720
He'll go after Rin if this keeps up.

160
00:21:05,120 --> 00:21:07,240
That's like letting Fire Phoenix kill him.

161
00:21:07,880 --> 00:21:10,400
- What about Rin?
- Fire Phoenix won't let her go either.

162
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:14,440
Killing two people

163
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:16,600
won't stop the virus.

164
00:21:19,880 --> 00:21:21,760
Taiga checked the lab again.

165
00:21:22,600 --> 00:21:23,520
Everything's gone.

166
00:21:24,360 --> 00:21:27,680
The lab, Techut, the chemists,

167
00:21:27,760 --> 00:21:29,760
everyone's vanished.

168
00:21:56,520 --> 00:21:57,560
Hey.

169
00:22:00,800 --> 00:22:03,480
Dad, help me.

170
00:22:04,720 --> 00:22:05,760
Who did this to you?

171
00:22:25,760 --> 00:22:26,920
It's you?

172
00:22:28,600 --> 00:22:30,480
How could you hurt your own child?

173
00:22:33,560 --> 00:22:34,400
Dad, don't!

174
00:22:40,080 --> 00:22:41,000
The pathogen.

175
00:22:45,600 --> 00:22:46,840
Don't kill Dad.

176
00:22:48,560 --> 00:22:49,640
Don't worry.

177
00:22:51,240 --> 00:22:52,600
I'll make the pathogen

178
00:22:52,680 --> 00:22:56,120
our child worked so hard to create
count for the most.

179
00:22:56,920 --> 00:22:59,320
You're worse than a beast.

180
00:22:59,400 --> 00:23:01,080
How can you kill your own blood?

181
00:23:04,320 --> 00:23:05,680
I'm not killing anyone.

182
00:23:06,360 --> 00:23:07,560
I'm not.

183
00:23:08,320 --> 00:23:09,760
I'm just testing.

184
00:23:10,600 --> 00:23:14,120
I don't even know
how these pathogens really work.

185
00:23:14,200 --> 00:23:16,280
You and our son
are just having fun on your own.

186
00:23:16,360 --> 00:23:18,200
Give the medicine to him right now!

187
00:23:18,280 --> 00:23:19,320
Medicine?

188
00:23:20,720 --> 00:23:22,200
Where is it?

189
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:24,640
I forgot.

190
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:28,200
You evil, despicable wretch!

191
00:23:31,240 --> 00:23:34,240
If you don't want to test the pathogen
on yourself too,

192
00:23:35,120 --> 00:23:37,760
then stop resisting.
Stop doing everything.

193
00:23:38,600 --> 00:23:41,920
Just rest, take care of each other
like father and son.

194
00:23:43,080 --> 00:23:44,600
You'll see

195
00:23:44,680 --> 00:23:48,760
how much I'm worth,
how important I am to 3C Corp.

196
00:24:26,720 --> 00:24:27,680
Dad.

197
00:24:28,800 --> 00:24:30,000
Help me.

198
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:43,000
Can you help me find Rin?

199
00:24:45,560 --> 00:24:48,320
Fire Phoenix isn't a place
you can just stumble upon.

200
00:25:02,040 --> 00:25:03,080
Dhammatat.

201
00:25:04,600 --> 00:25:05,720
Please help me find Rin.

202
00:25:06,240 --> 00:25:07,640
You've got to find her.

203
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:19,240
Who are these Fire Phoenix people?

204
00:25:19,320 --> 00:25:21,040
And why did they take Rin?

205
00:25:25,880 --> 00:25:29,200
Aru, we'll definitely find Rin.

206
00:25:29,800 --> 00:25:30,800
Give me a little time.

207
00:25:31,800 --> 00:25:34,600
When will it be?
What if Rin dies before we find her?

208
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:37,480
Please find her.

209
00:25:37,560 --> 00:25:39,560
Find her now. I'm begging you.

210
00:25:40,320 --> 00:25:41,640
- I'll even kneel if I have to.
- Aru.

211
00:25:41,720 --> 00:25:44,240
- Please help me find Rin.
- Okay.

212
00:25:53,080 --> 00:25:54,480
I can't get her location.

213
00:26:00,640 --> 00:26:02,040
Can you try one more time?

214
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:28,720
Kill me.

215
00:26:35,040 --> 00:26:37,200
Dying quickly isn't fun, Rin.

216
00:26:40,360 --> 00:26:41,880
Taiga's really possessive of you.

217
00:26:45,680 --> 00:26:47,240
Who's your boss?

218
00:26:48,800 --> 00:26:50,720
Suddenly asking about Damon?

219
00:26:52,520 --> 00:26:53,680
Why?

220
00:26:54,640 --> 00:26:55,880
Going to tell Taiga?

221
00:26:57,360 --> 00:26:58,600
Damon…

222
00:26:59,440 --> 00:27:00,960
isn't Naruban.

223
00:27:05,520 --> 00:27:07,680
That soft-hearted businessman.

224
00:27:07,760 --> 00:27:10,160
Think he's the Damon
ordering people killed?

225
00:27:12,720 --> 00:27:16,080
He's just a puppet,
being pulled left and right

226
00:27:17,360 --> 00:27:19,040
from behind.

227
00:27:20,400 --> 00:27:22,480
That face doesn't smile,

228
00:27:24,320 --> 00:27:26,120
because he hasn't felt anything in years.

229
00:27:32,800 --> 00:27:34,280
I never thought

230
00:27:36,440 --> 00:27:38,920
Naruban would make you so attached.

231
00:27:51,160 --> 00:27:53,600
Please let everyone know,
as we discussed in the meeting.

232
00:28:07,280 --> 00:28:10,480
Mom, the Hi app is ready to launch.

233
00:28:10,560 --> 00:28:12,720
I asked the board to help spread the word

234
00:28:12,800 --> 00:28:14,680
that you came up
with a lot of the app's ideas.

235
00:28:14,760 --> 00:28:17,120
Hey, don't make a big fuss.

236
00:28:17,200 --> 00:28:19,600
I like working behind the scenes,
keeping it low profile.

237
00:28:21,280 --> 00:28:23,200
It's your time to shine, Mom.

238
00:28:24,960 --> 00:28:26,080
Thanks, dear.

239
00:28:32,800 --> 00:28:35,600
Ratee said there's going to be
a change at 3C Corp.

240
00:28:35,680 --> 00:28:37,760
Mrs. Giranun's taking over for Naruban.

241
00:28:37,840 --> 00:28:40,000
All the more reason I need to go there.

242
00:28:40,080 --> 00:28:41,680
Why risk getting killed again, Taiga?

243
00:28:42,640 --> 00:28:44,480
If you go into 3C Corp.
and they take you out,

244
00:28:44,560 --> 00:28:45,840
vanish without a trace,

245
00:28:46,640 --> 00:28:47,680
who's going to help Rin?

246
00:28:48,840 --> 00:28:50,240
Shouldn't we focus on finding her?

247
00:30:03,160 --> 00:30:05,480
After the Hi app launch,

248
00:30:06,600 --> 00:30:08,320
3C Corp. won't have any traitors left.

249
00:30:11,720 --> 00:30:13,720
And Taiga, where is he?

250
00:30:15,240 --> 00:30:16,360
Taiga…

251
00:30:18,320 --> 00:30:19,680
He's in hiding.

252
00:30:21,760 --> 00:30:23,200
But I have bait.

253
00:30:27,960 --> 00:30:28,840
Rin, of course.

254
00:30:31,320 --> 00:30:32,640
He'll come looking.

255
00:30:33,440 --> 00:30:34,600
He won't let Rin die.

256
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:37,760
Love really can kill.

257
00:30:41,360 --> 00:30:42,400
And apparently,

258
00:30:43,120 --> 00:30:45,760
love can make someone powerful too.

259
00:30:52,560 --> 00:30:53,640
Thank you.

260
00:31:08,400 --> 00:31:09,480
Mr. Dhammatat.

261
00:31:11,600 --> 00:31:12,840
Where's Taiga?

262
00:31:14,480 --> 00:31:15,480
Weren't you watching him?

263
00:31:15,560 --> 00:31:16,880
I went to the bathroom.

264
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:23,360
You let Taiga go?

265
00:31:41,160 --> 00:31:42,440
Where's Rin?

266
00:31:42,520 --> 00:31:44,000
I should be asking you that.

267
00:31:44,880 --> 00:31:46,080
Fire Phoenix's going to kill her.

268
00:31:46,160 --> 00:31:47,880
Where could they be holding her?

269
00:31:49,600 --> 00:31:51,840
Fire Phoenix has multiple safe houses.

270
00:31:52,400 --> 00:31:56,240
It depends on the member to choose,
somewhere far from prying eyes.

271
00:32:02,920 --> 00:32:04,680
What are your hearts made of?

272
00:32:08,160 --> 00:32:11,480
Fire Phoenix destroys anyone
in the way of their power and wealth.

273
00:32:13,280 --> 00:32:15,800
They wipe out every business
that refuses to bow.

274
00:32:17,320 --> 00:32:19,520
Millions of innocent people,
what did they do

275
00:32:21,160 --> 00:32:23,280
to deserve being killed with disease?!

276
00:32:28,200 --> 00:32:29,040
Dad, watch out!

277
00:32:31,040 --> 00:32:31,840
Techut!

278
00:32:32,760 --> 00:32:33,600
Ugh!

279
00:32:33,680 --> 00:32:34,920
Techut!

280
00:32:35,920 --> 00:32:36,840
Hey!

281
00:32:38,480 --> 00:32:39,480
Techut!

282
00:32:40,600 --> 00:32:43,400
Pok, help me! Save my son!

283
00:32:58,400 --> 00:33:01,760
Where is your dad's hard drive, Lee? Huh?!

284
00:33:12,160 --> 00:33:13,160
Get the medicine, quickly.

285
00:33:13,760 --> 00:33:15,120
If not, he'll die.

286
00:33:16,600 --> 00:33:18,040
The medicine's been stolen.

287
00:33:19,440 --> 00:33:21,040
I'm looking for it too.

288
00:33:21,120 --> 00:33:22,400
How is that possible?

289
00:33:23,320 --> 00:33:25,240
You and your son control everything.

290
00:33:26,200 --> 00:33:28,200
But right now, I'm just a loser.

291
00:33:29,360 --> 00:33:31,960
I can't save my son, can't save anyone.

292
00:33:36,880 --> 00:33:38,360
I need to talk to you.

293
00:33:49,240 --> 00:33:50,640
What do you mean?

294
00:33:54,240 --> 00:33:56,200
As soon as I get the medicine,
you'll be the first to know.

295
00:34:07,520 --> 00:34:09,199
You have a good heart,

296
00:34:11,080 --> 00:34:12,199
just like your father.

297
00:34:16,639 --> 00:34:18,040
That look,

298
00:34:19,040 --> 00:34:20,239
it's the same look as Prin's.

299
00:34:25,960 --> 00:34:27,280
I'm sorry.

300
00:34:34,040 --> 00:34:35,360
I'm sorry, Pok.

301
00:34:49,520 --> 00:34:52,159
I knew the day the hit on Kenji
was ordered,

302
00:34:53,440 --> 00:34:55,760
which means Fire Phoenix has found you.

303
00:34:57,400 --> 00:34:59,120
You know my family.

304
00:35:01,520 --> 00:35:03,280
You know how they died.

305
00:35:06,440 --> 00:35:07,680
I couldn't do anything.

306
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:10,640
I couldn't protect my friends.

307
00:35:12,560 --> 00:35:14,840
I had to endure their control.

308
00:35:15,400 --> 00:35:18,280
They took 3C Corp., raked in profits,

309
00:35:18,360 --> 00:35:19,800
and did terrible things.

310
00:35:22,120 --> 00:35:25,400
I thought Prin's family
was completely gone.

311
00:35:44,320 --> 00:35:46,200
Until the day you came to 3C Corp.,

312
00:35:49,200 --> 00:35:50,560
the look in your eyes,

313
00:35:52,080 --> 00:35:54,680
it was like Prin demanding justice.

314
00:35:56,960 --> 00:35:59,720
Why did I let his family die?

315
00:36:03,680 --> 00:36:06,080
This is all I could do to protect you.

316
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:11,280
I couldn't let anyone
know your true identity.

317
00:36:13,320 --> 00:36:14,360
Not even Rin.

318
00:36:16,880 --> 00:36:20,320
Rin is a Fire Phoenix agent,
sent to watch me.

319
00:36:25,400 --> 00:36:27,920
I know Rin protects me sincerely.

320
00:36:29,440 --> 00:36:31,680
She's risked herself for me
more than once.

321
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:33,960
Who ordered you to do all this?

322
00:36:38,240 --> 00:36:39,200
Damon.

323
00:36:41,040 --> 00:36:42,360
The head of Fire Phoenix.

324
00:36:44,120 --> 00:36:45,200
Who is he?

325
00:36:46,040 --> 00:36:47,320
Where is he?

326
00:36:49,240 --> 00:36:50,680
No one knows.

327
00:36:51,480 --> 00:36:52,920
No one's ever seen Damon.

328
00:36:53,760 --> 00:36:56,680
He disguises his voice,
gives orders through email.

329
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:05,360
I don't have much time left.

330
00:37:07,200 --> 00:37:08,160
Pok.

331
00:37:09,480 --> 00:37:12,920
If I die, help Techut.

332
00:37:13,600 --> 00:37:15,160
Help my son survive.

333
00:37:20,000 --> 00:37:21,360
Your son uses power,

334
00:37:22,320 --> 00:37:23,320
money,

335
00:37:24,280 --> 00:37:26,240
even disease to kill innocents.

336
00:37:27,240 --> 00:37:30,000
Now you're begging someone else
to save your own son?

337
00:37:32,080 --> 00:37:34,560
I prayed just one of Prin's children
would survive.

338
00:37:36,560 --> 00:37:38,280
Then I met you first, Pok.

339
00:37:41,280 --> 00:37:42,880
All three of Prin's children

340
00:37:43,840 --> 00:37:44,800
survived.

341
00:37:46,920 --> 00:37:48,320
Khanin helped you.

342
00:37:49,160 --> 00:37:50,840
Prab and Pun also had help.

343
00:37:52,600 --> 00:37:54,640
Fire Phoenix spread news they were dead,

344
00:37:54,720 --> 00:37:56,920
so they could quietly hunt the kids.

345
00:37:59,840 --> 00:38:00,800
Prab.

346
00:38:02,000 --> 00:38:02,920
Pun.

347
00:38:07,440 --> 00:38:08,680
Where are my brothers?

348
00:38:13,960 --> 00:38:15,080
Where are they?

349
00:38:16,200 --> 00:38:17,800
I'm asking, where are my brothers?!

350
00:38:17,880 --> 00:38:18,800
I don't know!

351
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:23,600
But right now, Fire Phoenix
won't let any of you survive.

352
00:38:40,760 --> 00:38:43,360
Where is your dad's Fire Phoenix case
hard drive?

353
00:38:43,440 --> 00:38:45,920
- I already gave it to you.
- That's a fake!

354
00:38:50,640 --> 00:38:52,720
Are you willing to die, Lee?

355
00:38:53,360 --> 00:38:55,240
Die just because you believe
a man loves you?

356
00:38:58,760 --> 00:39:00,560
Just because Taiga acted selflessly,

357
00:39:01,080 --> 00:39:04,400
risking his life to deliver the medicine,
you think he really loves you?

358
00:39:06,320 --> 00:39:08,080
I didn't raise you to be this naive.

359
00:39:11,080 --> 00:39:12,960
Taiga will never love Fire Phoenix.

360
00:39:13,040 --> 00:39:14,120
Everything he does

361
00:39:14,200 --> 00:39:16,480
is to kill us, one by one.

362
00:39:16,560 --> 00:39:19,560
And eventually,
he'll fire the gun right here

363
00:39:19,640 --> 00:39:21,520
the moment you're no longer useful!

364
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:23,520
Then just kill me!

365
00:39:24,760 --> 00:39:27,640
If I die, Taiga can't kill you.

366
00:39:30,920 --> 00:39:32,760
Soft-hearted because of love, huh?

367
00:39:41,600 --> 00:39:42,760
Fine.

368
00:39:44,640 --> 00:39:46,160
Then don't die yet.

369
00:39:46,880 --> 00:39:48,480
Watch Taiga die first.

370
00:39:49,600 --> 00:39:51,040
Then you'll see

371
00:39:51,120 --> 00:39:53,360
how poisonous love can ruin you
and wreck your life.

372
00:40:31,920 --> 00:40:35,120
How is that possible? Techut was poisoned?

373
00:40:35,200 --> 00:40:37,480
And the medicine was stolen?
I don't buy it.

374
00:40:38,720 --> 00:40:40,760
Naruban wants the medicine
to save his son too.

375
00:40:41,440 --> 00:40:43,720
These people,
all they care about is money,

376
00:40:43,800 --> 00:40:45,520
fame, and success.

377
00:40:45,600 --> 00:40:49,520
They put themselves at the center
and force the world to spin around them.

378
00:40:49,600 --> 00:40:51,800
They decided to create a deadly virus,

379
00:40:52,480 --> 00:40:54,360
put a price on human life in coins.

380
00:40:54,440 --> 00:40:56,440
The world's in chaos

381
00:40:56,520 --> 00:40:57,840
because the talented are evil.

382
00:40:58,480 --> 00:40:59,600
Karma's coming for them.

383
00:41:02,200 --> 00:41:04,360
We need the medicine fast, to save Rin.

384
00:41:06,920 --> 00:41:07,760
And Techut too.

385
00:41:08,680 --> 00:41:10,080
I won't let him die.

386
00:41:11,680 --> 00:41:13,520
He hasn't faced justice yet.

387
00:41:24,520 --> 00:41:26,840
When did Mr. Naruban collapse?

388
00:41:26,920 --> 00:41:27,920
Why are you only telling me now?

389
00:41:28,000 --> 00:41:31,400
His heart isn't doing well.
He should be admitted to a hospital.

390
00:41:40,240 --> 00:41:41,280
He can stay here.

391
00:41:41,360 --> 00:41:43,320
We have staff watching him all the time.

392
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:45,200
It's better to be close to the equipment.

393
00:41:45,280 --> 00:41:46,920
Mr. Naruban requested it.

394
00:42:02,680 --> 00:42:05,000
While I'm here, Giranun
can't force me to sign anything

395
00:42:05,560 --> 00:42:07,280
until I leave the hospital.

396
00:42:09,080 --> 00:42:10,920
How long do you think you can stall?

397
00:42:13,680 --> 00:42:15,760
If Giranun wants your position,

398
00:42:15,840 --> 00:42:18,280
she just calls a meeting
and picks a new CEO.

399
00:42:21,280 --> 00:42:22,480
It's not that simple.

400
00:42:23,400 --> 00:42:26,080
Trust isn't built in a day.

401
00:42:27,760 --> 00:42:31,400
Everyone's seen Giranun
as just a pretty face,

402
00:42:31,480 --> 00:42:32,840
no responsibility.

403
00:42:36,920 --> 00:42:37,920
Taiga.

404
00:42:39,120 --> 00:42:41,400
Block everything at 3C Corp. for now.

405
00:42:42,040 --> 00:42:43,040
I'm begging you.

406
00:42:45,400 --> 00:42:46,600
I'll help you.

407
00:42:48,600 --> 00:42:50,440
I'll get the medicine for Techut.

408
00:42:51,440 --> 00:42:52,880
But I need an answer.

409
00:42:54,560 --> 00:42:56,840
Where did Punlop lock Rin up?

410
00:43:35,360 --> 00:43:36,440
Go quickly!

411
00:43:43,040 --> 00:43:47,600
Good thing Dhammatat
disguised Sun's and my keycards.

412
00:43:48,200 --> 00:43:50,120
Otherwise, we couldn't reach this floor.

413
00:43:52,560 --> 00:43:54,360
Mr. Taiga's room is this way.

414
00:43:54,440 --> 00:43:55,440
Wait.

415
00:43:58,320 --> 00:43:59,680
Which way is Naruban's room?

416
00:44:29,600 --> 00:44:30,960
What are you doing in here?

417
00:44:33,080 --> 00:44:35,520
<i>The flash drive in your office</i>
<i>has been stolen.</i>

418
00:44:35,600 --> 00:44:39,520
The flash drive is linked
to each member's access code.

419
00:44:39,600 --> 00:44:41,960
But more than the data, it's the mask.

420
00:44:42,480 --> 00:44:43,320
Who are you really working for?

421
00:44:54,280 --> 00:44:55,560
Punlop.

422
00:45:26,720 --> 00:45:28,680
Subtitle translation by:
Chomchanach Yanaharn
